snippet.textDisplay:
It's stuff like this that defines the very soul of Coke Studio Pakistan... Excellent composition and instrumental settings are exemplary! And man, Ali Hamza's voice has such a mature texture! Kudos to Noor Zehra, and also the backup vocalists... Especially Rachel Viccaji... I'm guessing there's hardly any CSP performance where she hasn't rocked :)
Bless you all!
